<TITLE>BLACK MOON - METROPOLIS, an animation masterpiece by Rintaro</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" Content="... based on a manga by Osamu Tezuka.">

<META Name="keywords" CONTENT="Metropolis, Tezuka Osamu, Tezuka, Rintaro, Hayashi Shigeyuki, Otomo Katsuhiro, Fritz Lang, Akira, Ken-ichi, Tima, Duke Red, Detective Shunsaku Ban, Astro Boy, Kimba the White Lion, Galaxy Express 999, Record of Lodoss War, Revolution, Honda Toshiyuki, James Cameron, Titanic, Aliens, Terminator, Ridley Scott, Blade Runner, Steven Spielberg, AI, A.I., Forbidden Planet, Science Fiction, Robot, Android, Dixieland Jazz, Metropolitan Rhythm Kings, Louis Armstrong, Bix Beiderbecke, Cab Calloway, St. James Infirmary, Kurt Weill, Three Penny Opera, Egyptian Theatre, film review, anime review, Japanese film, Japanese movie, manga, anime, animation, the Blackmoon, the Black Moon.">

